Misc Search and replace pound or hash sign # I wanted to change a H3 header (###) in a markdown file. I first tried the ordinary search field (no regex) but I did not get any matches. What worked for me was to enable the regex search and enter the following:
^#{3}\sBuild system dir ~/&lsquo;Library/Application Support/Sublime Text 3/Packages/User&rsquo;
